snippet.title: King of Snatchers Story Trailer
snippet.description:
King of Snatchers is a story-driven multiplayer snatching game where players will try to complete an investigative quest by an AI. Through this gaming platform, the AI will be able to gather data regarding a catastrophe set to happen in the future. Players will compete to snatch important data.
